{"title":"春到法卡山","authors":["王晋军"],"dates":[{"year":1984,"month":4,"day":13}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"春到法卡山"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"王晋军"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一张春的照片"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在法卡山阵地，胡耀邦总书记亲切地邀一名小战士和他一起合影留念。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是真的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是真的，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总书记拉着我的手，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总书记和我唠家常，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总书记来到我身边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，春风就在我身边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"阳光就在我身边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"力量就在我身边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"信念就在我身边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"亲切的询问和叮嘱呀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一齐响在我耳边！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抚我戴的钢盔帽，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"红星闪闪放新颜；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"摸我挎的冲锋枪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"利刃铮铮敌胆寒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问我“你是哪里人？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一股暖流涌心间；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"问我“过节想家不？”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我涨红了脸儿表誓言："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青山处处埋忠骨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"好儿男，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"志在四方戍边关！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"没有大家无小家，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"不经苦涩哪来甜，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"为了祖国得安宁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"流血牺牲也心甘！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"贺年爆竹声声脆，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新绿新芽发满山。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"总书记就在我身边。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一声“咔嚓”遂心愿；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胸贴照片巡逻去，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我向祖国报春安……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一行春的题字"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"胡耀邦总书记饱蘸浓墨，为边防部队题字：“法卡山英雄山”"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“法卡山英雄山”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"锋利遒劲耸如山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“法卡山英雄山”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"深情厚意重如山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“法卡山英雄山”，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"崇高评价高于山；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"“法卡山英雄山”。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"无限期望大于山！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"南天一柱何壮哉，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"历史选择了法卡山："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"正义在这里发出怒吼。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"尊严在这里无法侵犯。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"理想在这里艰难生长。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"青春在这里承受重担。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"从井冈山到法卡山——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"战士们一如既往，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"山若人，人若山，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有山一样的勇敢，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"都有山一样的信念！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"雄关漫道真如铁，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"路转峰回总向前。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"一行关于山的题字，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"预示了一个关于山的春天："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"新的造山运动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将发生在伟大时代；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"更多英雄峰峦，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"将崛起在人民心间！"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":8,"page_end":8}